name: Rebel Gunrunner
Lore: 'Smugglers from many worlds are hunted by the Empire for providing arms and supplies to the Alliance. The Outer Rim is their refuge.',
Text: 'Deploy on table; and stack a non-lightsaber weapon (without ''lost'' in game text) here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If a battle was just initiated, may deploy weapon here on a participating card. Return weapon here at end of weapons segment (if possible), at end of battle, or if it is about to leave table, be stolen, or become inactive. (Immune to Alter).',
